quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  68,16,Aray nde Men maandina mo e hoore kinal
  68,17,"Men jarribor …ìe wano Men jarribornoo jey…ìe ngesa mba : fewndo …ìen woondunoo pellet, …ìe so√±ay mba subaka ko …ìe dawu…ìe"
  68,18,"…ìe ittintinaali [wiide] :\"Si Allah ja…ìii"
  68,19,Yiite immori ka Joomi maa ari huu…ìiti mba tawi hi…ìe …óaanii
  68,20,mba wa'iti wa jemma …ìaleejo
  68,21,∆Åe noddindiri bimmbi on
  68,22,"Kori dawee ka ngesa mon, si tawii ko on so√±oo…ìe"
  68,23,∆Åe hucciti hi…ìe …ì…óuumbo
  68,24,"Wonnde \"Miskiino woo naatataa e mabba hannde"
  68,25,"∆Åe ndawidi e …óawugol [waasu…ìe …ìen] ko …ìe e…ì…ìu…ìe"
  68,26,"Nde …ìe yi'unoo mba, …ìe wi'i: \"Pellet, men majjii [laawol ngol]"
  68,27,wurin ko men …óawaa…ìe
  68,28,"∆Åur…óo …ìe mo∆¥∆¥ude on wi'i: \"Mi wi'anaano on : haanii ko subbunhino…óon"
  68,29,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Senaade woodanii Joomi amen ! Pellet, hari ko men too√±u…ìe"
  68,30,"Wo…ó…ìe e ma…ì…ìe fewtiti …ìeya, hi…ìe felindira"
  68,31,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Ee bone amen ! Pellet, hari ko men bewu…ìe"
  68,32,"Hino gasa ka Joomi amen wattitana men …ìuri mban …óon mo∆¥∆¥ude. Ko ka Joomi amen ko min reer…óube e [yaafeede]"
  68,33,"Ko non tigi woni lette …óen; ko lette laakara …óen non …ìuri manude, sinno hi…ìe anndunoo"
  68,34,"Pellet, hino woodani gom…óu…ìe …ìen ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe, Aljannaaji neema"
  68,35,Kere Men wa…óay jebbilii…ìe …ìen wano bom…ìe …ìen
  68,36,"Ko he…ìi on, si …óon √±aawira non"
  68,37,"Kaa hi…óon mari Deftere, nde janngoton e mun"
  68,38,"Pellet, ko woodani on e mayre, ko ko su…ìoto…óon"
  68,39,"Kaa ko fodooje woodani on e Amen, hoolnii…óe haa √ëalnde Darngal, wonnde pellet, hino woodani on ko √±aawoton kon"
  68,40,Lamndii …ìe ko hommbo e ma…ì…ìe fawtanii…ìe …óum
  68,41,"Kaa ko kafidii…ìe woodani …ìe? Awa yo …ìe addu kafidii…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, si tawii ko …ìe goongu…ìe"
  68,42,"√ëalnde belenru √±oroytee, …ìe noddee e sujjugol kono hara …ìe waawataa. @Corrected"
